txt.en: You have discovered an outpouring of Orcs near the East Wall. You should defeat them for the good of Walstow.
'Any Orc that will no longer threaten my people brings me great joy.\n\n'You have done well in defeating our foes.'
Orcs have been spilling through the barricade at the East Wall, threatening the folk of Walstow and beyond. Their assault must be quelled.
Defeated Orcs near the East Wall ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Defeat Orcs near the East Wall ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

Winsig and her men have been facing great difficulty in containing the Orc invasion of the Sutcrofts from the East Wall.\n\nOrcs can be found near the pathway to the East Wall to the north of Walstow.
Winsig can be found inside the mead-hall of Walstow in south-eastern Sutcrofts.
